<br>
Ability to solo effectively. Does this class possess the tools to solo with an acceptable experience/downtime ratio to make soloing a viable option for experience gain?<br>
<br>
5 - Charm is an incredible skill for a well equiped (high hp/mana/charisma ) enchanter. Incredibly good.<br>
<br>
Ability to make money with innate abilities-Does this class possess innate skills or abilities that allow it to make money from other players outside of the melee setting?<br>
<br>
5 - The ability to make mana vials which are REQUIRED for other trade skills, creation of enchanted jewelry (while not in great demand at ). KEI. Incredibly good.<br>
<br>
Ability to make money through farming-Does this class possess the ability to farm items effectively enough to make it a viable option for making money?<br>
<br>
5 - Ive heard more than one story of how effective dire charm is for farming and I beleave them all.<br>
<br>
Group contribution- Does this class have a variety of skills which make it valuable in a group?<br>
<br>
5 - Slow, Haste, CC, Mana regen...<br>
<br>
Raid contribution-Does this class have a variety of skills which make it valuable in a raid setting?<br>
<br>
X - Good question. Havnt raided with my chanter so no response.<br>
<br>
Self-Sufficiency-Does this class possess the tools to travel safely, get out of trouble or does it have to rely heavily on other classes for survival? <br>
<br>
4 - Illusions, Invis, Speed enhancing spells, runes. Very good.<br>
<br>
Desirability in Groups-Is this a highly desired class for groups?<br>
<br>
5 - Either a chanter or shammy is REQUIRED for higher level XP groups.<br>
<br>
Perception of Class-How well is this class and the abilities of this class understood by other players?<br>
<br>
3 - Ive got a fairly good idea, however I've been in a LOT of groups that just dont have a clue.<br>
<br>
Equipment-Does this class have a good variety of equipment available to enhance it’s specific abilities?<br>
<br>
X - Not sure yet. Theres enough items out there for twinking though,,,,,,<br>
<br>
Expansions and Upgrades-Has this class received helpful new abilities/skills as the game has progressed?<br>
<br>
X - Not sure.<br>
<br>
Overall-Is this class properly balanced?<br>
<br>
4 - This applies just to the level Im playing at but having seen other enchanters in my guild go from 50-60 in under 2 weeks solo (post PoP) I strongly suspect so.<br>
